{
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "16.0",
      "line_index": 16,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f39d6746",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ＺＺＺ……ＺＺＺ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "23.0",
      "line_index": 23,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "13fb6120",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "まだ寝るには、少し早いと思うけど……もうぐっすり、おねむりになってる……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "23.4",
      "line_index": 23,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "13fb6120",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "最近お疲れだと、思ってたけど……本当だったみたい……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "28.0",
      "line_index": 28,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "20f2a974",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それなら未来のお嫁さんとして私がしっかりしないと……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "28.4",
      "line_index": 28,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "20f2a974",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "お疲れなら、やっぱりすっきり……しないとダメ、だよね",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "32.0",
      "line_index": 32,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "638d8054",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それならこの人が一番喜ぶ方法で……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "32.3",
      "line_index": 32,
      "inline_index": 3,
      "line_hash": "638d8054",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "うん、それがいい♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "42.0",
      "line_index": 42,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "29833251",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ん……んん……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "46.0",
      "line_index": 46,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "cca17fe6",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "（なん、だ……何か……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "49.0",
      "line_index": 49,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1258434f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "下腹部に違和感を覚え、眠っていた意識が徐々に目覚めていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "52.0",
      "line_index": 52,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7c1c880c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "（触られている……？　うう……ゾクゾク、する……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "55.0",
      "line_index": 55,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b5e396f9",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "寒気にも似た何かが背筋を駆け上り、全身が震えあがる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "56.0",
      "line_index": 56,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "72b1496c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "俺の反応に一瞬だけ違和感が消えるが、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "56.2",
      "line_index": 56,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "72b1496c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "再び何かが下半身をまさぐる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "59.0",
      "line_index": 59,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b16b5191",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "（ああ……何だか気持ち、良い……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "62.0",
      "line_index": 62,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e8ecbd15",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "下半身が浮くような気持ち良さに、勝手に腰が跳ね上がる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "63.0",
      "line_index": 63,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b8684656",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "気持ち良さにさらに意識が目覚めていくと、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "63.2",
      "line_index": 63,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "b8684656",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "微かに声が耳に入ってくる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "71.0",
      "line_index": 71,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4dd89d1",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "すごい……♥　こんなに大きく……♥　やっぱりお疲れなんだ……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "74.0",
      "line_index": 74,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "454e977",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "（……誰？　声が……ああ……これ誰かがチンポ触って──）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "78.0",
      "line_index": 78,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ff97c676",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "──れるぅ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "81.0",
      "line_index": 81,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c296494e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "──んおおっ！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "96.0",
      "line_index": 96,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a3dc8b22",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ルミナっ！？　な、何をして……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "100.0",
      "line_index": 100,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "54c3291a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あ……♥　起きちゃった？♥　れるっ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "103.0",
      "line_index": 103,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2ba8ea03",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "うあ……！　ちょ、ちょっと……ううううっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "106.0",
      "line_index": 106,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1f45d60",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "肉棒を舐められる感触に驚き、眠気が一気に吹き飛ぶ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "107.0",
      "line_index": 107,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "30482293",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そんな俺のことなど意に介さず、ぺろぺろと肉棒を舐め続けるルミナ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "109.0",
      "line_index": 109,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d1dc319b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ざらざらの小さな舌で裏筋から鈴口を舐められ、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "109.2",
      "line_index": 109,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "d1dc319b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "腰が浮きそうになるほどの快感が襲ってくる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "112.0",
      "line_index": 112,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7da45d1a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ルミナ、そんなこと舐めたらダメだって……うっ……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "116.0",
      "line_index": 116,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "52e0a0b4",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "なんで？　おちんちんぺろぺろしたらダメなの？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "116.2",
      "line_index": 116,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "52e0a0b4",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "私、あなたのこと大好きなのに……♥　ちゅ……ちゅぅっ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "119.0",
      "line_index": 119,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b5c13c59",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "うう！　そ、その気持ちはすごい嬉しいけど……くっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "119.2",
      "line_index": 119,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "b5c13c59",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "で、でも汚いだろ……？　だから……んんっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "123.0",
      "line_index": 123,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3a5179f9",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そんなことは、ない♥　汚いなんて、微塵も思わないよ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "123.2",
      "line_index": 123,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "3a5179f9",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あなたのモノって思うだけで、すごく愛おしく思えてくるから……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "126.0",
      "line_index": 126,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "532c4ac1",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それにこれは、結婚後のれんしゅー……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "126.2",
      "line_index": 126,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "532c4ac1",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "お嫁さんは毎晩お婿さんのおちんちんをぺろぺろするの♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "134.0",
      "line_index": 134,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a02343db",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ちゅ……れる♥　れるぅ……♥　れろっ♥　れるんっ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "137.0",
      "line_index": 137,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "28975eb5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ぐっ……！　あ、あああ……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "140.0",
      "line_index": 140,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c6c911bd",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "小さな手が肉竿を扱き始め、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "140.2",
      "line_index": 140,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "c6c911bd",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "二重の気持ち良さに両脚がガクガクと震える。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "142.0",
      "line_index": 142,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6ba57c8f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そんな俺の反応にルミナは微笑む。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "143.0",
      "line_index": 143,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d7316668",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "幼さと大人っぽさの入り混じった笑みに、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "143.2",
      "line_index": 143,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "d7316668",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "胸がドクンと一際大きく高鳴る。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "146.0",
      "line_index": 146,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "badc8f79",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "エッチなお汁溢れてきた♥　勉強したとおりだね♥　れる……れるっ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "149.0",
      "line_index": 149,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "52e9eedb",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ちょっとしょっぱい……♥　でも全然不快な気持ちにはならないよ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "149.2",
      "line_index": 149,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "52e9eedb",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "もっと……もっとおちんちん感じて……♥　気持ち良くなって♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "151.0",
      "line_index": 151,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4ab99b9f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ルミナが亀頭を舐め上げるたびに、喉の奥から声が漏れ出す。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "152.0",
      "line_index": 152,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "15198a36",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "思わず腰を捩ってしまうが、ルミナは体重を掛け腰を抑える。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "154.0",
      "line_index": 154,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4f86e264",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "溢れる先走りを迷いなく舐めとり、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "154.2",
      "line_index": 154,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "4f86e264",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "その姿を見ているだけで興奮で頭がどうにかなってしまいそうになる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "157.0",
      "line_index": 157,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "84c763a8",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あなたのおちんちんおいしー♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "157.2",
      "line_index": 157,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "84c763a8",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "愛する人のおちんちんだからなの、かな？♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "157.4",
      "line_index": 157,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "84c763a8",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ずっとずっとこうしていたい……♥　あなたにいっぱい……ご奉仕したい♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "160.0",
      "line_index": 160,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "59c10018",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "くっ！　ルミナ、そんな強く扱かれると……くううっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "163.0",
      "line_index": 163,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "59d2f1f6",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "懸命に竿を扱き、嬉しそうに亀頭を舐め回していくルミナ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "165.0",
      "line_index": 165,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f011df86",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "一生懸命に奉仕してくるその姿に根負けし、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "165.2",
      "line_index": 165,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "f011df86",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "俺はそっとルミナの頬を撫でる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "168.0",
      "line_index": 168,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "fb781ba4",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ふふ♥　あなた今すごく優しい瞳をしている……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "168.2",
      "line_index": 168,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "fb781ba4",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "わたし、あなたのそんな瞳が大好き……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "171.0",
      "line_index": 171,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "db5b18d3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ルミナだって同じだよ。可愛らしくて優しさに溢れて……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "171.2",
      "line_index": 171,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "db5b18d3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "すごくエッチな瞳になってる",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "175.0",
      "line_index": 175,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "96f0ea55",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ふふふ♥　わたしがエッチだから",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "175.2",
      "line_index": 175,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "96f0ea55",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あなたのおちんちんがこんなになっているんだね♥　嬉しい♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "177.0",
      "line_index": 177,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "deee1e38",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ルミナは自身の喜びを伝えるように、さらに舌を大きく這わせる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "178.0",
      "line_index": 178,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e4475b5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "指先がカリ首に触れ、肉棒がルミナの手の中で大きく跳ねる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "181.0",
      "line_index": 181,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c2af8c54",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ここ男の人の弱点なんだよね♥　本に書いてあったよ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "181.2",
      "line_index": 181,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "c2af8c54",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "いっぱいシコシコしてあげるね♥　ちゅ……♥　れるぅ、ちゅるぅ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "183.0",
      "line_index": 183,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "72df18a5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "小刻みにカリ首を擦り上げられ、その刺激で射精感が一気に高まる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "186.0",
      "line_index": 186,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3a4c2760",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ルミナ……ううっ！　そろそろ射精そう……くっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "190.0",
      "line_index": 190,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "44d84e80",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "いいよ、いつでも出して♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "193.0",
      "line_index": 193,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d803a31f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "でもそのままルミナの顔が汚れてしまうから……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "197.0",
      "line_index": 197,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f72388b9",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "全然構わないよ♥　だから遠慮しないで射精して♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "197.2",
      "line_index": 197,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "f72388b9",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "れろぉ♥　ちゅ♥　ちゅっ♥　んぢゅるぅ♥　ちゅちゅぅぅ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "200.0",
      "line_index": 200,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2166225b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "んぅぅぅ！　ルミナ……！　う、う、うう！　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "200.2",
      "line_index": 200,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "2166225b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "もう……うあ、ああああ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "212.0",
      "line_index": 212,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "84843",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ふあぁっ！？♥　ああ、出た……これがあなたの……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "212.2",
      "line_index": 212,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "84843",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "す、すごい……白くてベトベトなのいっぱい出てるぅ……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "214.0",
      "line_index": 214,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3f6e3dd2",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "勢いよく出た精液がルミナの綺麗な顔を真っ白に汚す。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "215.0",
      "line_index": 215,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ef037dd8",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "その光景に異様なまでに興奮が高ぶり、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "215.2",
      "line_index": 215,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "ef037dd8",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "熱いモノが何度も陰茎を駆け上がる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "218.0",
      "line_index": 218,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "263afadc",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "くはぁ……！　ルミナ、ごめん、顔に……はーっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "222.0",
      "line_index": 222,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "be7a7dba",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ふふっ♥　気にしなくてもだいじょーぶだよ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "222.2",
      "line_index": 222,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "be7a7dba",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "こんなにたくさん出たってことは、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "222.4",
      "line_index": 222,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "be7a7dba",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それだけ私で感じてくれたってことだよね？♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "225.0",
      "line_index": 225,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b0aecd38",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あ、ああ……最高に気持ち良かった……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "225.2",
      "line_index": 225,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "b0aecd38",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "こんな射精初めてかもしれない……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "229.0",
      "line_index": 229,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d9ea17dc",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そう言ってもらえて嬉しい♥　ねぇ、あなたの精液飲んでもいい？♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "232.0",
      "line_index": 232,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d943738f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そ、それはやめておいた方がいいって。すごい不味いと思うし",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "236.0",
      "line_index": 236,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "96fd31c4",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "んー……でもあなたが出したモノだから……れるっ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "238.0",
      "line_index": 238,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7f7e4ddb",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ルミナは躊躇なく鈴口に溢れていた白濁液を舌で舐めとる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "241.0",
      "line_index": 241,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f65ec132",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "きゃうっ！？♥　今またちょっと出た♥　感じちゃった？♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "244.0",
      "line_index": 244,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "11b0ff32",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あ、ああ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "244.2",
      "line_index": 244,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "11b0ff32",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ルミナが俺のを舐めたって思うだけで感じて……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "244.4",
      "line_index": 244,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "11b0ff32",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "だいじょうぶだった？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "248.0",
      "line_index": 248,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6eeeac86",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "うん、だいじょうぶ♥　でも精液の味ちょっと変わってる♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "248.2",
      "line_index": 248,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "6eeeac86",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "苦くて正直あまり……でもあなたのだと思うと……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "248.4",
      "line_index": 248,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "6eeeac86",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "んちゅ……れる、ぺろ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "251.0",
      "line_index": 251,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "406a1b90",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "もっと欲しいって……そう思えてくるよ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "251.2",
      "line_index": 251,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "406a1b90",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ねぇ……もう一回してもいい？♥　あなたにもっと感じてほしい……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "254.0",
      "line_index": 254,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "681cd700",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ルミナ……わかった、もう一度お願い……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "254.2",
      "line_index": 254,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "681cd700",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "もう一度ルミナに感じさせてほしい",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "258.0",
      "line_index": 258,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c0639504",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ありがとう♥　それじゃあいっぱい気持ち良くなって♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "258.2",
      "line_index": 258,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "c0639504",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "一生懸命感じさせるから、またいっぱいぴゅってして♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "266.0",
      "line_index": 266,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d9c7f19c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "れるぅ♥　ぺろ♥　んちゅ……れるぅ♥　ちゅ♥　ちゅぅ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "269.0",
      "line_index": 269,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e9b4a6c0",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ああ……！　ルミナ……くうっ、うう……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "272.0",
      "line_index": 272,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "439d590b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ルミナは陰茎を扱き始め、同時に亀頭の精液をぺろぺろと舐め取る。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "273.0",
      "line_index": 273,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f612f9c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "熱の籠ったフェラと手コキが、過敏になっている肉棒を強く刺激していく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "276.0",
      "line_index": 276,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "662b813a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "かわいい声♥　もっとその声聞きたい♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "279.0",
      "line_index": 279,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "633283a0",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "くう……！　んあ……ちょ……はげしいって……うううっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "283.0",
      "line_index": 283,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "cc74565d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あなたの感じる仕草、すごく色っぽくてドキドキしてくる……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "283.2",
      "line_index": 283,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "cc74565d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "身体、熱い……♥　はぁ……はぁ♥　ちゅ……ちゅぅ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "285.0",
      "line_index": 285,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b4f5b9e4",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "息を荒くしながらも、懸命にフェラを続けるルミナ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "286.0",
      "line_index": 286,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9de82282",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "手コキもどんどんリズミカルになり、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "286.2",
      "line_index": 286,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "9de82282",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "搾り出されるように先走りが溢れる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "288.0",
      "line_index": 288,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "fc23f2f7",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "俺が声を上げるたびに色っぽく微笑み、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "289.0",
      "line_index": 289,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e5382ed1",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ルミナのそんな表情に完全に心奪われてしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "292.0",
      "line_index": 292,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "40b06845",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "お汁すごく溢れて……♥　いっぱい感じてくれて嬉しいよ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "292.2",
      "line_index": 292,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "40b06845",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ちゅ……ちゅ……ちゅぅぅぅっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "295.0",
      "line_index": 295,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "979c2ea9",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あぁ！　う、あ……ああーっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "298.0",
      "line_index": 298,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a32dfefc",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "吸い出すように先走りを舐め取られ、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "298.2",
      "line_index": 298,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "a32dfefc",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "背筋がくの字になるほど反り返る。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "299.0",
      "line_index": 299,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2ecdd1d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "睾丸がムズムズとし始め、再び射精感がこみ上げてくる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "302.0",
      "line_index": 302,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "fd0ff64",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ルミナ……！！　ま、また出そうだ……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "302.2",
      "line_index": 302,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "fd0ff64",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "もう一回ルミナの顔真っ白に汚させてくれ……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "305.0",
      "line_index": 305,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d018c323",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "俺は心の奥底で思っていたドス黒い願望をルミナに伝えてしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "306.0",
      "line_index": 306,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d75cd122",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そんな俺にルミナは嫌な顔一つ見せず微笑む。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "309.0",
      "line_index": 309,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6fb95552",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "うん、いいよ♥　いっぱいぴゅってして♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "311.0",
      "line_index": 311,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ab8ad7d3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ルミナはさらに力強く肉棒を扱き、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "311.2",
      "line_index": 311,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "ab8ad7d3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そして小さな舌を目いっぱい大きく動かす。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "312.0",
      "line_index": 312,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c1558c46",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "亀頭全体を舐め回され、さらに射精感が強くなっていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "315.0",
      "line_index": 315,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "27a839e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "もう射精る……！　く、ううぅっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "319.0",
      "line_index": 319,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2fa09e28",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "来て……♥　あなたの精液いっぱいかけて……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "322.0",
      "line_index": 322,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "fba136d2",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ルミナ……！　う、うううーーっ！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "334.0",
      "line_index": 334,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5b527f3d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ひゃぁっ！？♥　あああ、またすごい勢いで……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "334.2",
      "line_index": 334,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "5b527f3d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あ、熱い……♥　さっきよりいっぱい出てるぅ……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "336.0",
      "line_index": 336,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "55b2d2b7",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "限界までガマンした熱いモノが一気に陰茎を駆け上り、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "336.2",
      "line_index": 336,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "55b2d2b7",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ルミナの顔をびちゃびちゃと汚していく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "338.0",
      "line_index": 338,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1947ce2d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "真っ白なモノを黒く染め上げる、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "338.2",
      "line_index": 338,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "1947ce2d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そんな快感により興奮が高ぶり、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "338.4",
      "line_index": 338,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "1947ce2d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "何度も射精を繰り返し、ルミナを汚していく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "341.0",
      "line_index": 341,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4165a885",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "すごい、ね♥　お顔ベドベド……♥　こんなにいっぱい、嬉しい♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "341.2",
      "line_index": 341,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "4165a885",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あなたがこんなに出してくれて幸せだよぉ♥　はぁぁ～♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "344.0",
      "line_index": 344,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2b20fa30",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ルミナ……すごい気持ち良かった……もうそれしか感想が出てこない……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "347.0",
      "line_index": 347,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "358b340",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "射精も終わり、心地良い倦怠感が全身を包み込む。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "348.0",
      "line_index": 348,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9ef74ffc",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "今自分は世界で一番幸せ、そんなことを心の中で思ってしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "351.0",
      "line_index": 351,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "35a7c0bc",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ふふ♥　結婚したら毎日えっちしよーね♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "351.2",
      "line_index": 351,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "35a7c0bc",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "私がいっぱい気持ち良くしてあげるから♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "353.0",
      "line_index": 353,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6df91a9d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ルミナのお願いに俺は頷く。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "354.0",
      "line_index": 354,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f58c6570",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ルミナは俺の言葉に嬉しそうに微笑み、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "354.2",
      "line_index": 354,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "f58c6570",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "幸せを噛みしめるように肉棒の精液を舐め取っていくのであった。",
      "zh": ""
    }
  ]
}
